# ── Saxo Bank OpenAPI — PKCE OAuth2 configuration ────────────────────────────
#
# Step 1: Register a free app at https://developer.saxobank.com
#         → My Apps → Create app
#         Set redirect URI to:  http://localhost:8501/
#         No client secret is needed — this app uses PKCE (RFC 7636).
#
# Step 2: Copy Client ID below and save this file as .env
#
# Step 3: Run the app and click "Connect to Saxo Bank" in the Saxo Connect tab.
#
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# NEVER commit .env to git — it is already in .gitignore.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Required — app client ID from developer.saxobank.com
SAXO_CLIENT_ID=

# Optional overrides (defaults shown — change only if needed)
SAXO_REDIRECT_URI=http://localhost:8501/
SAXO_AUTH_BASE=https://sim.logonvalidation.net
SAXO_OPENAPI_BASE=https://gateway.saxobank.com/sim/openapi
